  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Heartburn twice a week for at least 2 years. Normal EGD and 24hr pH study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  &lt;18yrs of age,pregnant, unable or unwilling to give consent, allergic to PPI,
             previous gastric or esophageal surgery, past hx of erosive GERD, unwilling or unable
             to stop acid suppression meds
      </textblock>
